The Nike Revolution 5 shoes have a soft foam sole that will provide comfort while running. The upper is made of light and breathable textile material. The simple and unobtrusive design of the shoes will suit everyday life.

The sewn leather upholstery on the top is full of texture and gives traditional style, durability and support. Originally designed for sports hoops, the Nike Air shock absorber provides easy comfort all day long. The low silhouette gives a clean, streamlined look. The padded collar feels soft and comfortable.
The shoe has a familiar fit that runners love, with new forefoot cushioning and foam for maximum responsiveness. The result is a lightweight, durable workout shoe perfect for your daily run.
